8
00:01:24,799 --> 00:01:26,920
Luckily, I had Xu Siguo modify the carriage.

9
00:01:27,359 --> 00:01:28,760
Mobility's much better now.

10
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,599
What I mean is,

11
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:35,000
I think you misunderstood.

12
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,439
When I said "smash it,"

13
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:37,519
whatever that means,

14
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:39,560
from this moment on,

15
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:41,359
it's Black Street's job now.

16
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:44,280
I feel like

17
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:46,280
I'm still pretty useful, you know.

18
00:01:49,319 --> 00:01:49,879
Good luck.

19
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:55,640
Let's go.

20
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,799
Let's give a warm round of applause

21
00:02:07,799 --> 00:02:10,000
to welcome our host!

22
00:02:10,319 --> 00:02:12,000
Alright.

23
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,400
Oh, for heaven's sake!

24
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:15,520
What do you want now?

25
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,719
Sorry,

26
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:17,639
I'm in a hurry.

27
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,319
When's the draw today?

28
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,280
I promise,

29
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,280
I won't threaten you today.

30
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:23,800
We'll do the draw fair and square.

31
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:25,479
Today's the grand final.

32
00:02:25,479 --> 00:02:26,280
Just one match.

33
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,240
There's no draw.

34
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,439
No draw, huh.

35
00:02:31,919 --> 00:02:33,199
Then the match officially...

36
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:33,800
Wait.

37
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,840
After all, this is the grand final.

38
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,479
Look, none of the officials

39
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,360
have arrived yet.

40
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,639
Why don't you wait a bit?

41
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,120
How about

42
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:47,120
I take a look at the prize first?

43
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,120
A prize of this level,

44
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:50,240
I'm not even worthy to look at it.

45
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,520
Then how about another draw...

46
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,280
Hello, everyone.

47
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,599
Quite the grand entrance.

48
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,360
This guy,

49
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:06,599
he was insufferable back in school.

50
00:03:06,919 --> 00:03:07,719
Looking at him now,

51
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,560
he's even more revolting.

52
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:12,039
Hello, everyone.

53
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,599
I'm Gu Changkong.

54
00:03:14,599 --> 00:03:16,560
I'm delighted you could all join

55
00:03:16,879 --> 00:03:18,520
the Imperial Capital's inaugural

56
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:21,159
Path to Immortality Tournament.

57
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,199
As the host,

58
00:03:23,439 --> 00:03:24,879
we naturally uphold

59
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:26,599
a fair and impartial stance.

60
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:27,919
So,

61
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,479
for this grand final,

62
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:31,120
we, the Imperial Capital,

63
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,319
will only send out

64
00:03:32,599 --> 00:03:34,159
one contestant.

65
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,800
As long as the Shanhai City team

66
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,199
can defeat him,

67
00:03:38,639 --> 00:03:40,759
they'll win the grand championship

68
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:42,120
of this tournament.

69
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:52,120
This is the champion's prize.

70
00:03:53,319 --> 00:03:54,280
I can't wait to see

71
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:55,719
who this prize

72
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:57,759
will ultimately go to.

73
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,599
Let the match begin!

74
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:17,519
Why don't you have any teammates?

75
00:04:17,959 --> 00:04:18,879
In this mortal world,

76
00:04:19,199 --> 00:04:20,519
no one is worthy yet

77
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,759
to be my teammate.

78
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:23,439
I get it.

79
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,879
You're a show-off with no friends.

80
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,360
I'm in a hurry.

81
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,920
Let's make this quick.

82
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:29,680
I hope you're worthy enough

83
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,079
to make me summon an immortal.

84
00:04:31,879 --> 00:04:33,000
Speed: Tier Three.

85
00:04:56,879 --> 00:04:58,079
Is this all you've got?

86
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:02,639
Sangou,

87
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:05,360
I'll leave the award ceremony to you.

88
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:07,240
I trust that with your skills,

89
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,079
you can definitely retrieve what's inside.

90
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,360
What?

91
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,800
You don't want the Divine Blessing anymore?

92
00:05:19,639 --> 00:05:21,160
If I'm not mistaken,

93
00:05:22,199 --> 00:05:23,959
