94
00:05:24,199 --> 00:05:24,959
I'll die.

95
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,319
Am I right?

96
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:46,839
What are you talking about?

97
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,519
The box is empty.

98
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:51,319
After you showed the artifact to everyone,

99
00:05:51,319 --> 00:05:52,439
you took it away.

100
00:05:54,319 --> 00:05:55,040
This trick?

101
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,959
I knew it when I was four.

102
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,160
Looks like I underestimated you.

103
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:07,079
You're smarter than I thought.

104
00:06:09,399 --> 00:06:10,519
I can sense it.

105
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,360
You have a bigger scheme in play.

106
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:13,879
Now you

107
00:06:14,079 --> 00:06:15,920
are worthy of knowing my name.

108
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:16,920
I am

109
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:17,920
Haotian.

110
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:20,879
Is "Hao" even a real surname?

111
00:06:21,439 --> 00:06:22,519
Ignorant mortal.

112
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:25,360
The match ends here.

113
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,079
Will you accept the award yourself,

114
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:30,079
or shall my men escort you there?

115
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:32,519
Don't worry.

116
00:06:33,319 --> 00:06:34,959
In front of everyone,

117
00:06:35,199 --> 00:06:37,319
I'll stage your silencing.

118
00:06:39,399 --> 00:06:41,319
I just came here to slack off.

119
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:45,000
Didn't expect to hook a shark.

120
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,000
Mighty is the Lord on high,

121
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:47,040
gazing down in splendor,

122
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,160
watching over the four directions,

123
00:06:48,399 --> 00:06:49,360
seeking the people's peace.

124
00:06:49,839 --> 00:06:50,600
Haotian's

125
00:06:50,759 --> 00:06:51,480
Divine Radiance!

126
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,000
You know what?

127
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,519
Outside Black Street,

128
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:00,560
people call me Boss Dog.

129
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:01,800
And besides,

130
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,120
being this close to me

131
00:07:03,639 --> 00:07:04,600
is very dangerous.

132
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,600
Even with a Divine Blessing,

133
00:07:33,759 --> 00:07:34,959
you're still this useless?

134
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:36,920
That kinda hurt.

135
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:38,959
You're too weak.

136
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:43,319
First time I've seen a maniac

137
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:45,319
get pummeled like this.

138
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:48,120
He can't actually be losing, can he?

139
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:51,959
Did you see the look in his eyes?

140
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:53,360
He's just toying with him.

141
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,040
This idiot.

142
00:08:00,279 --> 00:08:01,759
Going crazy at the worst possible time.

143
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,920
Is now really the time to play around?

144
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,399
He's playing.

145
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,439
He just loves playing around.

146
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:08,519
Taking this long for a single fight.

147
00:08:08,839 --> 00:08:09,720
So tedious.

148
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:25,120
Guards!

149
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:50,960
Hurry up! Don't run!

150
00:08:51,039 --> 00:08:51,639
Move!

151
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:26,399
A weapon?

152
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:27,840
I've got one too.

153
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,679
Strength: Tier Seven.

154
00:10:08,559 --> 00:10:09,320
Just as I

155
00:10:10,039 --> 00:10:11,240
