156
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:13,600
You can't handle Tier Seven.

157
00:10:14,639 --> 00:10:17,120
You dare make me kneel before you?

158
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:18,919
Haotian's might

159
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:20,600
