160
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:21,879
Don't try to play the victim here.

161
00:10:21,919 --> 00:10:22,960
I just hit you once.

162
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,840
You knelt on your own.

163
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:24,759
Not my fault.

164
00:10:24,799 --> 00:10:25,759
You dissipated the force yourself

165
00:10:25,759 --> 00:10:26,600
