166
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,360
If you don't believe me, let's reenact it.

167
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,799
This is exactly how I hit you.

168
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,960
Celestial Punishment, transform!

169
00:10:58,879 --> 00:11:00,679
If I were the one on that stage,

170
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:03,320
