176
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:16,919
That's all in the past now.

177
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:29,000
Mortals are mortals after all.

178
00:11:56,399 --> 00:11:57,240
Get him!

179
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:35,240
So this is what you call

180
00:12:35,759 --> 00:12:37,080
Celestial Punishment?

181
00:13:03,879 --> 00:13:04,519
No.

182
00:13:05,559 --> 00:13:06,360
Impossible.

183
00:13:07,279 --> 00:13:09,080
No one survives Celestial Punishment.

184
00:13:10,519 --> 00:13:11,240
You

185
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,000
are defeated.

186
00:13:33,879 --> 00:13:34,919
You lost.

187
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:37,960
Call me Boss Dog.

